Inheritance
	allows you to create a class that is a refinement or a specialisation of 
	antoher class.
	use of is- a relationships.

Mixins
	provides the ability of mixing in methods in classes.
	through modules
	use for is-able-to relationships.

Composition
	when an object achieves its behavior by containing another object.
	Use for has-a relationships. 

Dependency injection
	An injection is the passing of a dependency(an object) to a dependent object
	(a client). The object is made part of the client's state. 

Duck Types
	for behaves-like-a relationships.
